snippet.title: Satan is an Astronaut Game Trailer
snippet.description:
Satan is an Astronaut is a new Visual Novel originally made for Spooktober 2023 Visual Novel Game Jam. 

You can play the first two chapters now at https://demeru.itch.io/satanisanastronaut for free. We have plans to continue developing the story and adding more content for you to experience.
